Now i know why food king did not feature katong chicken rice in their best chicken rice episode. I was like, what where is katong chicken rice?!?!?!

title: Food King Singapore: The Best Chicken Rice in Singapore! (Finally allowed us to feature them!)
comment:
Now i know why food king did not feature katong chicken rice in their best chicken rice episode. I was like, what where is katong chicken rice?!?!?! 

Another thing about their chicken rice is that they don use the knife to pat the meat flat before cutting it. I think by doing that, the meat is thick, juicy and substantial when u bite into it. 

And yes their soup is like some super elixir where after u drink it, u feel like all ur ailments are healed.
